title: One bedroom with built-in buffet and video tour!
posting_body: ['1941 Aldrich is an adorable apartment building located right off W Franklin Ave, right between Hennepin and Lyndale - close proximity to nearly anywhere you would want to go!', 'It is even walking distance from iconic Uptown restaurants and fun!', 'This one-bedroom apartment is the perfect blend of original character with modern details!', 'Available October 1st, this apartment will surely rent fast!', 'So come see it today!', 'Features include:', 'Stunning Hardwood Floors', 'Original Built-In and Wood Details', 'Claw Foot Tub', 'Spacious', 'Charm', 'Rent: $945', 'Deposit: $945', 'Application Fee: $40', 'Heat, water, and trash are included in the monthly rent!', 'Check out the video tour of the exact unit!', 'https://youtu.be/pHG_G_AJhUE', 'Be sure to check out our website for rental criteria and additional available units:', '<URL>', 'Locally owned and professionally managed by IrvingProperties.', 'Give us a call or email to see our homes:', 'show contact info']
